               <p>I lodge in the same house the prisoner lodges in: upon the 22d of November the prisoner coming home at night called for a light; I lit him; he took out a deal box about two<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177701150044"></xptr> foot long, well corded, and carried it into his room.</p>
               <p>- Bridges, the husband of the last witness, and 
